text: Marcel Hotz (born 18 May 1966) is a Swiss rower. He competed in the men's coxed four event at the 1988 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1966 births Category:Living people Category:Swiss male rowers Category:Olympic rowers of Switzerland Category:Rowers at the 1988 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
